<subSubSection pageId="27" pageNumber="88" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="27.[136,1452,158,761]" pageId="27" pageNumber="88">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,316,158,184]" pageId="27" pageNumber="88">Etymology</emphasis>
:—The specific epithet is named in honor of Dr. Ching-I Peng, mentor and collaborator of the senior author, for his continuous guidance, supports, and friendship, and for his great contribution to the studies of Asian Flora.
